org.apache.samoa.core

Interface EntranceProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.github.javacliparser.Configurable, Processor, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClusteringEntranceProcessor, HelloWorldSourceProcessor, PrequentialSourceProcessor

    public interface EntranceProcessor
extends Serializable, com.github.javacliparser.Configurable, Processor
    An EntranceProcessor is a specific kind of processor dedicated to providing events to inject in the topology. It can be connected to a single output stream.
